# ADR inventory ritual

## When this applies

Any edit under **`docs/adr/`** that adds, renames, or changes **`ADR-*.md`**.

## Required steps

1. Run **`.\scripts\inv-adr.ps1`** from repo root (or rely on **`new-adr.ps1`**, which invokes it after scaffold).
2. Stage **`docs/adr/INVENTORY.txt`** in the **same commit/PR** as the ADR change.
3. Optional operator attestation: **`ssh-keygen -Y sign -f <key> -n file docs/adr/INVENTORY.txt`** and commit **`INVENTORY.txt.sig`** when publishing evidence.

## Agent guardrail

- **Do not** merge a PR that changes **`ADR-*.md`** without an updated **`INVENTORY.txt`**.
- If pytest **`test_adr_inventory_sync`** fails, regenerate inventory before push.

